## 1. DEVICE IDENTIFICATION:
id: m5stack-core-s3
name: "M5Stack CoreS3"
manufacturer: M5Stack
mcu: "ESP32-S3 Xtensa LX7 dual-core up to 240 MHz; 16MB Flash; 8MB PSRAM Quad; Wi-Fi 2.4 GHz; BLE 5.0; 2.0in 320x240 ILI9342C cap-touch; GC0308 camera; AXP2101 PMU; BMI270 IMU; BM8563 RTC; AW88298 1W I2S amp (G13 DOUT/G14 DIN/G34 BCK/G33 WCK/G0 MCLK); ES7210 dual-mic; 500mAh LiPo; DinBase"
category: maker
image: m5stack-core-s3.svg
url: "https://docs.m5stack.com/en/core/CoreS3"

